name: Vintage Santa Claus - CUSTOM Address Labels or Stickers
description:
A wonderful vintage Santa label!!
 
SIZE: 
You can get these in 1.5" round (30 per sheet) or 2" round (20 per sheet.) If no size is indicated in Notes to Seller, the 1.5" size will be sent. This listing is for ONE SHEET of self adhesive labels.
 
After completing the checkout processs, please send an email to tracisimsdesigns at gmail dot com with the following information:
 ✒ Label size - 1.5" or 2" round labels 
✒ Text for personalization 
✒ Make sure you type it *EXACTLY* as you would like it to appear - including any capitalization, or lack thereof
 
PROOF: 
A digital proof will be sent to you by email for approval. I will work with you until we get your design right!
 
A NOTE ABOUT COLOR: 
Colors vary on different monitors. What I see on mine may not be exactly what you see on yours. Please take this into consideration when ordering. While I do my best to ensure correct colors, cannot guarantee that what you receive will have the exact colors of what you see on your screen.
 
Please allow 2-3 business days for printing prior to shipping, but I can usually get these out much sooner.
